Watch Jamie Dornan and Dakota Johnson Get Steamy in a Crowded Elevator in New 'Fifty Shades Darker' Clip 
Subtle. By Sarah Lindig Jan 29, 2017 This weekend has been absolutely awful —so, here's a new Fifty Shades Darker teaser, in case you need to take a break from it all (and perhaps get a few ideas for Valentine's Day plans...) The latest clip from the upcoming film highlights what date night looks like for Anastasia Steele and Christian Grey. It starts with a romantic dinner, then—in classic Fifty Shades form—quickly shifts to risqué as Jamie Dornan's commanding Christian tells Dakota Johnson's blushing Anastasia to remove her underwear right there at the table. "Check, please!" Advertisement - Continue Reading Below Things then move into the elevator where some more steamy action takes place—in complete disregard of the several people standing nearby—as Taylor Swift and Zayn Malik's song "I Don't Wanna Live Forever" plays, setting just the right mood for this provocative scene.
